34075 0 obj<</Subj(Text Box)/Type/Annot/P 5 0 R/F 4/C[]/CreationDate(D:20260212142104-07'00')/T(jpjen)/Subtype/FreeText/Rect[1641.443 404.7081 2009.617 582.308]/DA(1 1 1 rg /Helv 8 Tf)/DS(font: Helvetica 8pt; text-align:left; margin:1pt; line-height:9.2pt; color:#000000)/M(D:20260217211701-07'00')/RC(<?xml version="1.0"?><body xmlns:xfa="http://www.xfa.org/schema/xfa-data/1.0/" xfa:contentType="text/html" xfa:APIVersion="BluebeamPDFRevu:2018" xfa:spec="2.2.0" style="font:Helvetica 8pt; text-align:left; margin:1pt; line-height:9.2pt; color:#000000" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><p style="color:#000000; text-align:left">1. DIAGRAM IS CONCEPTUAL AND FOR PRELIMINARY DESIGN ONLY.</p><p /><p>2. FINAL EQUIPMENT RATINGS SUBJECT TO SHORT-CIRCUIT, LOAD FLOW, AND COORDINATION STUDIES.</p><p /><p>3. PROTECTION, CONTROL, AND METERING NOT SHOWN; TO BE DEFINED IN DETAILED DESIGN PER UTILITY REQUIREMENTS.</p><p /><p>4. GROUNDING SYSTEM TO BE DESIGNED PER IEEE AND UTILITY STANDARDS.</p><p /><p>5. AUXILIARY POWER SYSTEM CONFIGURATION AND SIZING SUBJECT TO MANUFACTURER DATA AND FINAL LOAD CALCULATIONS.</p><p /><p>6. BUS CONFIGURATIONS AND INTERCONNECTION ARRANGEMENT SUBJECT TO UTILITY APPROVAL.</p><p /><p /><p /><p /></body>)/Contents<>/BS<</W 0/S/S/Type/Border>>/AP<</N 34077 0 R>>/NM(WCJDFEDJCAPVMNRM)>>
endobj
